She looked at Quickstrike and Stingra. She heard what Stingra said to 
Quicktrike.  Shge felt sorry for him.  She turned her head to look at 
Scorponok.  She liked him.  She wanted him to bfe happy with her.  She 
looked back at Quickstrike.  She wanted to comfort him but felt like it was 
not her place to interfere with his relationships.  She just lowered her 
head and worked on the console.

She looked at Quickstrike and said in a low voice.
"Is everything alright commander? Is there anything I can do for you?"
She wanted to make him happy.  Blast her programming, not only did she have 
to obey, but she liked both of them.  She felt benieth both of her 
commanders and not worthy of either, but wanted to please both.
